      {
        "start": "00:02.100",
        "end": "00:04.500",
        "original": "ラミィ、悩んでる顔してどうしたの？",
        "english": "Lamy, why do you look so troubled?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:04.900",
        "end": "00:06.000",
        "original": "あ、かなたん！",
        "english": "Ah, Kanatan!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:06.400",
        "end": "00:11.500",
        "original": "そうなの。ヒーローってどうあるべきか分かんなくなっちゃって。",
        "english": "That's right. I've become unsure of what a hero should be.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:12.300",
        "end": "00:14.300",
        "original": "力があるだけじゃだめなんだ。",
        "english": "Strength alone isn't enough.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:14.500",
        "end": "00:17.800",
        "original": "大事なのは、その力をどう使うかだよ。",
        "english": "What's important is how you use that strength.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:18.500",
        "end": "00:19.500",
        "original": "かなたん。",
        "english": "Kanatan.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:20.500",
        "end": "00:23.500",
        "original": "握力だけじゃ、世界は変えられない。",
        "english": "Grip strength alone can't change the world.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:24.100",
        "end": "00:28.500",
        "original": "人々の心を守るのも、ヒーローの大事な大事な仕事なんだから。",
        "english": "Protecting people's hearts is also a very, very important part of a hero's job.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:29.500",
        "end": "00:33.500",
        "original": "そっか。力で守れないものもあるよね。",
        "english": "I see. There are things strength can't protect, right?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:34.500",
        "end": "00:38.200",
        "original": "さ。だから、ヒーローにも強い心が必要なんだ。",
        "english": "Yes. That's why a hero also needs a strong heart.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:38.800",
        "end": "00:43.800",
        "original": "どんなにピンチになっても、乗り越えるたびにどんどん強くなる心が。",
        "english": "A heart that gets stronger and stronger every time you overcome a crisis, no matter how dire.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:44.200",
        "end": "00:48.000",
        "original": "さ、僕と一緒に歌って、強い心を掴み取ろう！",
        "english": "Now, let's sing together and seize that strong heart!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
