      },
      {
        "start": "04:22.300",
        "end": "04:24.000",
        "original": "(Chu wa)",
        "english": "(Chu wa)",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:27.800",
        "end": "04:32.300",
        "original": "ありがとう、かなたん。なんとなくヒーローって何かっていうのを掴めた気がするよ。",
        "english": "Thank you, Kanatan. I feel like I've finally grasped what it means to be a hero.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:33.300",
        "end": "04:37.000",
        "original": "よかった。きっとラミィなら素敵なヒーローになれるよ。",
        "english": "I'm glad. I'm sure you'll become a wonderful hero, Lamy.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:37.500",
        "end": "04:41.000",
        "original": "その人を思いやる気持ちを忘れずにね。",
        "english": "Just don't forget to be compassionate toward others.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:41.500",
        "end": "04:46.300",
        "original": "分かった。ラミィなりのヒーロー像、考えてみるよ。ありがとう！",
        "english": "Got it. I'll think about my own ideal of a hero. Thank you!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:47.300",
        "end": "04:49.000",
        "original": "それじゃ、さらば！",
        "english": "In that case, farewell!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:52.300",
        "end": "04:54.500",
        "original": "あ、行っちゃった。",
        "english": "Ah, she's gone.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:55.300",
        "end": "05:01.000",
        "original": "よし！この調子で次に行くぞー！",
        "english": "Alright! I'm going to keep this momentum and move on to the next part!",
